Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.03,0:03:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请妳期待吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.57,0:03:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好 晚上好等妳好久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.78,0:03:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们等妳好久了 过来吧 大家都在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.45,0:03:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都等好久了你们好 好淫荡的屁股阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.79,0:03:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么呀 大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.86,0:04:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都等好久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.46,0:04:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?情欲的味道 真厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.67,0:04:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么突然吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.34,0:04:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个什么味道呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.61,0:04:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的屁股 屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.01,0:04:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是色情阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部也挺厉害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.22,0:04:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也是好色情的 等等啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.75,0:04:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有阴毛呢大家看看呀 这个好色情呢 讨厌啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.49,0:04:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢 我看看 打开看看 好真色情阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.30,0:04:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真色情啊 怎么样阿?在面被这梯对待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.44,0:04:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上的这个候在外面这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.71,0:04:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很紧张呢 真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.24,0:04:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好期待吧 好期待呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.38,0:04:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想肉棒吗? 肉棒 是呀 很想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.45,0:04:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要肉棒吧？不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.92,0:05:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里吗？妳真是变态阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.66,0:05:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在外面哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.99,0:05:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里吗？嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里吗？嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.13,0:05:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.67,0:05:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.41,0:05:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部都大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我们看看吧 看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.75,0:05:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳乳头硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.22,0:05:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔软吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.83,0:05:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻阿 接吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.63,0:05:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不错的味道阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.78,0:06:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害,好兴奋阿 我可以插入嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.66,0:06:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.46,0:06:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.34,0:06:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？ 太突然了吗？ 可是没事的没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.21,0:06:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你插入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.36,0:06:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我舔肉棒阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.43,0:06:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.85,0:07:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.18,0:07:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是淫荡阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.19,0:07:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断的有感觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.19,0:07:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.73,0:07:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有感觉这里也好厉害呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.80,0:07:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽阿 有很多肉棒哟 太爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.93,0:07:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽快吗?大爽快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.81,0:07:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行真愉快呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.94,0:07:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.41,0:07:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.68,0:07:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边还有哟 继续阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我舔肉棒阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.23,0:07:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的手帮我套弄肉棒呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.77,0:08:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不错呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.91,0:08:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部真柔软阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.65,0:08:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有三根了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.13,0:08:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根根都好硬呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样被肉棒夹住爽快吗？ 再靠近一点阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.27,0:08:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有好多肉棒哟 把个脱吧 给我们看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.75,0:08:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是什么阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.35,0:08:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太淫荡了 都露出来了 淫荡的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.22,0:08:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看呀 太淫荡了 吻我阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.96,0:08:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.16,0:09:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个味道太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来啊 趴下去 把屁股翘起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.12,0:09:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.39,0:09:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错吧? 是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.73,0:09:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 可是我 里面有这个露来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.40,0:09:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏梨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.54,0:09:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把腿起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.28,0:09:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.77,0:10:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.51,0:10:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隰透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.33,0:10:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 这里有感觉是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.00,0:10:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.76,0:11:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害阿 我都兴奋起来了 好想插入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.56,0:11:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧? 这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.50,0:11:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒可以插入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.50,0:11:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这多肉棒 太厉害了 这边也帮忙摸摸呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.44,0:11:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.78,0:11:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨乳呀 巨乳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.76,0:12:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了 要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.10,0:12:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.53,0:12:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我摸阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.66,0:12:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换下根肉棒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.27,0:13:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.81,0:13:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.89,0:13:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样阿？爽快吧？ 好厉害 这样的太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有好多哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.04,0:13:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大了 太爽快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.72,0:13:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.59,0:13:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.07,0:14:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有肉棒要妳舔的哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.14,0:14:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就保持这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样不要动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.41,0:14:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我舔肉棒吧 我也来插入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙舔这边的肉棒阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哟 来舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.11,0:14:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 先停一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.86,0:15:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转一下 转个方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.83,0:15:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断在旋转哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的肉棒帮忙舔阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.78,0:15:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下来点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.06,0:16:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要转了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 帮我含进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.16,0:16:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽阿 好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.36,0:16:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害阿妳从来没有试过 这样的吧？没有 大多肉棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超爽的 爽快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穴满满的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.45,0:17:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要尽情享受哟 太快了 转到这边了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.65,0:17:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又转了 还有好多哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.75,0:17:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽快吗？ 很爽快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.49,0:17:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.43,0:17:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧我阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.97,0:18:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧我阿 这样会超爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.72,0:18:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏梨怎么阿? 好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.39,0:18:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快感不断的传过来 好爽阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.40,0:18:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱紧我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.80,0:18:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.94,0:18:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.67,0:18:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们过去 要过去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.48,0:18:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多了太爽快了 爽快吧 还很多哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.23,0:18:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒 肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.03,0:19:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插入这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.63,0:19:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插入这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多肉棒阿
