Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.38,0:20:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换我来吧 我也想插入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.58,0:20:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点插入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.58,0:20:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插入吧插入
