Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.24,0:21:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.04,0:21:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也有哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.05,0:21:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉售阿 好爽阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.85,0:21:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个太爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.72,0:21:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽阿
